Package org.gitlab.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GitlabAPIClient
    This class implements Gitlab API client that keeps endpoint, HTTP request configurations, and authentication information (in the form of tokens).
    GitlabAPIClient.Builder
    This Builder is used to build GitlabAPIClient instance.
    GitlabBranch
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Branch.
    GitlabBranch.ProjectQuery
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query for GitlabBranches within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range.
    GitlabCommit
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Commit.
    GitlabCommit.ProjectQuery
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query for GitlabCommits within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range.
    GitlabIssue
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Issue.
    GitlabIssue.ProjectQuery
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query issues within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range.
    GitlabIssue.Query
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global GitlabIssues with searching scope and range.
    GitlabMergeRequest
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Merge Request.
    GitlabMergeRequest.ProjectQuery
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query merge requests within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range.
    GitlabMergeRequest.Query
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global GitlabMergeRequests with searching scope and range.
    GitlabProject
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Project.
    GitlabProject.Query
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global projects.
    GitlabProject.UserQuery
    Class to query GitlabProject owned by a specific user
    GitlabUser
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component User.
    GitlabUser.ProjectQuery
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query users within a GitlabProject.
    GitlabUser.Query
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global users.
    Pagination
    This is the class that represents a pagination with page number and page size.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AuthMethod
    This is an Enum class to represent all types of authentication methods to authenticate with Gitlab API.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    GitlabException
    Signals that an exception occurring during invoking Gitlab REST API.
